title: MisterMusic Show 297 -NEW indie,alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 297 - (2 hours) 192kbps MP3 stereo



New music from The Black Keys, The Pains of Being Pure at Heart,
Band of Skulls, Mimicking Birds and Kaiser Chiefs on this episode.

Plus a big modern rock and mainstream top ten hit from 1999,  that people
know--but many don't know the actual title, is the Oldie of the Week.

It is a blast of new indie and alternative music with over 5 decades of hits
broadcasting weekly, and heard globally- The MisterMusic Show.



The MisterMusic Show is heard weekly on Rock XS Radio.


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
